<subSubSection pageId="149" pageNumber="547" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="149.[1393,2599,293,449]" pageId="149" pageNumber="547">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1395,1743,293,326]" pageId="149" pageNumber="547">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. At present, very little is known of the Thin Mouse Shrew; further studies are needed. The species may be threatened by habitat destruction.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
